alerts.headline: Wind Advisory issued December 8 at 12:11AM PST until December 8 at 10:00AM PST by NWS Los Angeles/Oxnard CA
alerts.description:
* WHAT...Northeast winds 10 to 15 mph with gusts up to 30 mph
expected.

* WHERE...San Luis Obispo County Beaches and San Luis Obispo County
Inland Central Coast.

* WHEN...Until 10 AM PST this morning.

* IMPACTS...Gusty winds will blow around unsecured objects. Tree
limbs could be blown down and a few power outages may result.
